Currently in the custom tools documentation (https://docs.griptape.ai/stable/griptape-tools/custom-tools/) it demonstrates passing parameters through a `params` parameter:

```python
    def generate(self, params: dict) -> TextArtifact:
        return TextArtifact(str(round(random.random(), params["values"].get("decimals"))))
```

But in the past few releases it's been possible to pass the parameter directly:

```python
    def generate(self, decimals: int) -> TextArtifact:
        return TextArtifact(str(round(random.random(), decimals)))
```

we should update the docs to demonstrate both options

